### Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/api/health

### Envoyer OTP
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+22370000001"
}

### Vérifier OTP (remplacer le code par celui affiché dans la console)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+22370000001",
  "code": "123456",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Refresh Token (remplacer par votre refresh token)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "VOTRE_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### Lister catégories
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/categories

### Lister quartiers
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/quartiers

### Lister prestataires (publique)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/providers?limit=10

### Lister prestataires par catégorie
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/providers?categorySlug=coiffure

### Détail prestataire (remplacer ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/providers/PROVIDER_ID

### Mon profil (requiert auth)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer VOTRE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Admin - Statistiques
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Admin - Liste prestataires
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin/providers?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Admin - Vérifier prestataire
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin/providers/PROVIDER_ID/verify
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Admin - Suspendre prestataire
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin/providers/PROVIDER_ID/suspend
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "suspended": true
}
